data.description: BIG PRICE IMPROVEMENT! A SLICE OF PARADISE IS AWAITING! Welcome to your dream RANCH-STYLE home situated on 1.03 acres of picturesque land on a Cul-de-sac! This stunning 4 bedroom/3 bathroom CUSTOM BUILT HOME (2019) is waiting for you! This home was designed for entertaining and privacy and is extremely well maintained. As you enter, you will be greeted with the perfectly laid travertine tile throughout the home. The split floor plan offers a private owner's retreat with an ensuite bath, dual sink vanity, separate shower, and two walk-in closets by California Closet. The Owner's retreat is spacious enough to allow a couch or a massage chair. You will be fascinated with your private door from the Owner's retreat to access the back lanai. Perfectly situated to allow a quiet and quick escape on a cool night to count stars! There are two bedrooms near the front of the house, divided nicely by a full-size bathroom with a tub. Towards the back of the house is a Bedroom and full-size bathroom, perfect for any guest or teenager to enjoy some privacy. The Bedrooms are accented with wood-like ceramic tile and coffered ceilings throughout the home. The owners spared no expense! Be sure to take notice of the appointments throughout the home - the 8" baseboards, crown molding throughout, plantation blinds, and so much more! The property features many places to gather or spaces to slip away for a time to enjoy your favorite hobbies, from its reading rooms, dens, and oversized library/office room with tons of shelves and storage for just about any series and collections. At the estate's center is its magnificent one-of-a-kind luxurious kitchen, which features granite counters, beautiful wood cabinetry, accents on the counters, and ample storage space that spills over into the separate den/library/office. Hidden away in the kitchen, is a ginormous walk-in pantry that will be a favorite place to store your unused items to keep clutter aside to showcase this kitchen’s elegance. Kitchen appliances are all state-of-the-art and lightly used. This kitchen is a CHEF's DREAM! The home exudes elegance with a casual sitting/great room, ideal for entertaining guests, and a separate formal dining room adjacent to the spacious galley kitchen. Enjoy your morning coffee at the breakfast bar, overlooking the main living room, which boasts of sunlight beaming through the sliding glass doors that lead to your private backyard oasis. The property also has a spacious laundry room equipped with a large capacity washer and dryer and an oversized mud room. Some appliances are gas: stove, water heater, and washer and dryer. owners take such pride in every home component: Gas Tank serviced by: Amerigas, March 2022, Filled Quarterly. Well serviced/inspected: March 2022. Septic Tank serviced by Brandon Septic, July 2022, and Cleaned/Pumped, March 2022. Water Treatment serviced by Culligan, and routine maintenance, is completed quarterly. AC serviced by Veteran Air, August 2023. Service will occur Oct 2023 and April 2024. HOA FEES are only $250 A YEAR!!! You are PERFECTLY LOCATED between Tampa, Sarasota, and St. Pete for a QUICK COMMUTE anywhere. There are so many BEAUTIFUL BEACHES that are close by. Recent Appraisal supports NEW PRICE! Sellers are willing to contribute $5,000 in closing costs or a buydown rate with an accepted offer.
